      "solution": "According to the question, 16 + 64 – 4 × 4 + 3 = ?. So, 16 + 64 ÷ 4 – 4 × 3 = ? ⇒ 16 + 16 – 4 × 3 = ? ⇒ 16 + 16 – 12 = ? ⇒ 32 – 12 = ? ∴ ? = 20 (using VBODMAS rule)"
